Class UserDirectoryService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sakaiproject.user.cover.UserDirectoryService
  • Deprecated. 
    Static covers should not be used in favour of injection or lookup via the component manager. This cover will be removed in a later version of the Kernel

extends Object

    UserDirectoryService is a static Cover for the UserDirectoryService; see that interface for usage details.
